Darkness Radio Presents: Supernatural News/Parashare: The Mandela Effect is on My Bucket List Edition with Mallie Fox!

It's been a crazy week in the world of Supernatural News!  Elon Musk says if Russia shuts the engines off n the ISS, HE GOT DIS! Do you remember using the term, "The Bucket List" before the 2007 movie, if so, when? Let's start talking MANDELA EFFECT! AND, If the Queen of England is close to the end (Heaven forbid), we tell you about the spirits she may be seeing!! 

Check out Mallie's website here: https://www.paranormalgirl.com/
